data.description: Spacious rooms, lots of storage, and room to expand! New furnace and new carpet throughout this updated 3 bedroom, 3 bathroom home, with a 1 car garage. Featuring a combined kitchen and dining room, this home provides a great open concept space that is ideal for entertaining. The basement has been partially finished to include insulation and an egress window, ready for the addition of another bedroom and bathroom, or other finished space of your choice! Centrally located, this house is just minutes from entertainment, shopping, and many other amenities. Schedule your showing today, before it's gone!
